{
  "text": "Comparison with published expression data (KLL/DNL expression). Expression data from ref. [CITATION_1] were used to generate a comparison data set of gene expression changes in glioblastoma versus normal brain (n = 8 samples). Statistical significance of overexpression or underexpression in glioblastoma relative to normal brain was set at P < 0.05.",
  "correct_citation": {
